window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The latest thrilling and emotional Alpha and Omega novel from the number-one </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author of the Mercy Thompson series.</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>Charles Cornick is the son of the leader of the North American werewolves - and his father's enforcer. Anna Latham, a rare Omega wolf with a calming presence, is his mate. They go where they are needed, handling problems in werewolf packs throughout the country. But this time the danger is closer to home, as an enemy armed with witchcraft threatens Charles and Anna's own pack.&nbsp;</p>"; 
